---

import mainImage from "../../assets/about/about1.png"; 
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
---

<section class="home-remodeling-experts-section">
  <div class="experts-content-wrapper">
    <h1 class="experts-main-title">Home Remodeling Experts <br /> in Maryland</h1>

    <div class="experts-columns-container">
      <div class="experts-image-column">
        <Image src={mainImage} alt="Home remodeling expert working on cabinets" class="experts-main-image" />
      </div>

      <div class="experts-text-column">
        <p>
          At Bethelor, we are dedicated to delivering high-quality home remodeling
          services across Maryland, including kitchen renovations, bathroom
          remodeling, and complete home improvement projects. Whether it's a small
          upgrade or a full transformation, we bring precision, passion, and personalized
          service to every home we touch.
        </p>
        <p>
          With years of hands-on experience, our team of skilled professionals takes
          pride in using smart design, modern trends, and durable materials to bring
          your vision to life. We believe that remodeling is not just about construction—
          it's about creating beautiful, functional spaces that improve your daily life.
        </p>

        <p class="commitment-text">What sets Bethelor apart is our commitment to:</p>
        <ul class="commitment-list">
          <li>Clear and honest communication from start to finish</li>
          <li>Attention to detail and custom-tailored solutions</li>
          <li>Respect for your home, time, and budget</li>
          <li>Lasting craftsmanship that adds real value to your property</li>
        </ul>

        <p class="serving-areas">
          • Serving Baltimore, Montgomery County, and surrounding areas.
        </p>

        <a href="#" class="request-quote-button">
          Request your free quote <span class="arrow-right">→</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
@import url("https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Sans:ital,opsz,wght@0,9..40,100..1000;1,9..40,100..1000&family=Host+Grotesk:ital,wght@0,300..800;1,300..800&display=swap");


.home-remodeling-experts-section {
  background-color: #ffffff; 
  padding: 100px 0; 
  font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
  color: #333333;
  box-sizing: border-box;
}

.experts-content-wrapper {
  max-width: 1400px; 
  margin: 0 auto; 
  padding: 0 40px;
  box-sizing: border-box;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column; 
  align-items: flex-start; 
}

.experts-main-title {
  font-family: 'Host Grotesk', sans-serif;
  font-size: 4.5em; /* Título grande */
  font-weight: 600;
  line-height: 1.1;
  color: #000000;
  margin: 0 0 50px 0px; 
  max-width: 800px; 
  padding-left: 20px; 
}

.experts-columns-container {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between; 
  align-items: flex-start; 
  gap: 60px; 
  width: 100%; 
}

.experts-image-column {
  flex: 1.2; 
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center; 
  align-items: flex-start;
}

.experts-main-image {
  max-width: 100%; 
  height: auto;
  display: block;
  box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  border-radius: 8px; 
}

.experts-text-column {
  flex: 1; 
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  justify-content: flex-start;
  align-items: flex-start;
  padding-top: 10px; 
}

.experts-text-column p {
  font-size: 14px;
  line-height: 1.6;
  color: #555555;
  margin-bottom: 20px;
}

.commitment-text {
  font-size: 15px;
  font-weight: 600;
  color: #333333;
  margin-bottom: 10px; 
}

.commitment-list {
  list-style: none; 
  padding: 0;
  margin: 0 0 20px 0; 
}

.commitment-list li {
  font-size: 14px;
  line-height: 1.5;
  color: #555555;
  margin-bottom: 8px; 
  position: relative;
  padding-left: 20px; 
}

.commitment-list li::before {
  content: "•";
  font-size: 1.2em;
  color: #000000; 
  position: absolute;
  left: 0;
  top: 0;
}

.serving-areas {
  font-size: 14px;
  line-height: 1.6;
  color: #555555;
  margin-top: 20px; 
  margin-bottom: 30px; 
}

.request-quote-button {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  background-color: #000000;
  color: #ffffff;
  padding: 12px 25px;
  text-decoration: none;
  font-size: 14px;
  transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
  border-radius: 4px; 
}

.request-quote-button:hover {
  background-color: #333333;
}

.request-quote-button .arrow-right {
  margin-left: 10px;
  font-size: 1.1em;
}

@media (max-width: 1024px) {
  .home-remodeling-experts-section {
    padding: 80px 0;
  }

  .experts-content-wrapper {
    padding: 0 30px; 
  }

  .experts-main-title {
    font-size: 3.5em; 
    margin-bottom: 40px;
    padding-left: 0; 
    text-align: center;
  }

  .experts-columns-container {
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 40px; 
  }

  .experts-image-column,
  .experts-text-column {
    flex: none; 
    width: 100%; 
    max-width: 650px;
    margin: 0 auto; 
    align-items: center; 
  }

  .experts-main-image {
    max-width: 90%; 
  }

  .experts-text-column p,
  .commitment-text,
  .serving-areas,
  .request-quote-button {
    text-align: center; 
    max-width: 90%; 
    margin-left: auto; 
    margin-right: auto;
  }

  .commitment-list {
    text-align: left; 
    max-width: 90%;
    margin-left: auto; 
    margin-right: auto;
  }

  .commitment-list li {
    padding-left: 25px; 
  }

  .commitment-list li::before {
    left: 5px; 
  }
}

@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .home-remodeling-experts-section {
    padding: 60px 0;
  }

  .experts-content-wrapper {
    padding: 0 20px;
  }

  .experts-main-title {
    font-size: 2.8em; 
    margin-bottom: 30px;
  }

  .experts-columns-container {
    gap: 30px; 
  }

  .experts-image-column,
  .experts-text-column {
    max-width: 500px;
  }

  .experts-main-image {
    max-width: 100%;
  }

  .experts-text-column p,
  .commitment-text,
  .serving-areas {
    font-size: 13px; 
    max-width: 100%; 
  }

  .commitment-list li {
    font-size: 13px; 
    padding-left: 20px;
  }

  .commitment-list li::before {
    left: 0;
  }

  .request-quote-button {
    padding: 10px 20px;
    font-size: 12px;
  }
}

@media (max-width: 480px) {
  .home-remodeling-experts-section {
    padding: 40px 0;
  }

  .experts-content-wrapper {
    padding: 0 15px;
  }

  .experts-main-title {
    font-size: 2.2em; 
    margin-bottom: 25px;
    line-height: 1.1;
  }

  .experts-columns-container {
    gap: 25px;
  }

  .experts-image-column,
  .experts-text-column {
    max-width: 350px;
  }

  .experts-text-column p,
  .commitment-text,
  .serving-areas,
  .commitment-list li {
    font-size: 12px;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .request-quote-button {
    padding: 8px 15px;
    font-size: 11px;
  }

  .request-quote-button .arrow-right {
    margin-left: 8px;
    font-size: 1em;
  }
}
</style>